parcel.description: Home of the Machi X DAO, a collective of artists and patrons, commissioning and trading digital art. The Machi X DAO is a member-directed organization where members pool resources, create proposals to improve Machi X, and approve governance changes for the Machi X ecosystem. Join our [discord](https://discord.gg/ZHtmzV5) to learn more.

### Machi X is a collective of artists and patrons, curating and trading digital art. 
We believe in bridging the gap between the crypto-native and mainstream world through art. With communal collaboration, we can make Machi X a fun and rewarding endeavor for all members.

G H O S T  A G E N T

## InfiNFT is our minting partner and Machi X is proud to be part of the Alpha launch. 
Nate and the InfiNFT team made this show possible by crafting the best NFT smart contract available anywhere, supporting more file types, sizes, metadata fields on-chain while immortalizing these pieces on the permaweb with the highest secure storage limits.
